high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right.
Pick up the ice cream scoop you see in front of you.
Take a step to your right.
Put the ice cream scoop in the bowl to the left of the lettuce.
Pick up the bowl with the ice cream scoop in it.
Turn right and take a half step right and one step forward.
Put the bowl in the cabinet under the right side of the sink and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with an ice cream scoop in it in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn right to the table.
Pick up the ladle off of the table.
Turn right and go farther down the table.
Set the ladle in the bowl on the table.
Pick up the bowl and ladle.
Turn to the right near the sink.
Open the cupboard under the sink and put away the ladle and bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put away the bowl and ladle in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, then turn right to face the table.
Pick up the large spoon from the table, next to the coffee maker.
Turn right, move forward, then turn left to face the table.
Put the large spoon in the bowl, behind the lettuce.
Pick up the bowl from the table.
Turn around, move forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the bowl in the right cabinet, beneath the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a large spoon in it in the cabinet.
